    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, making it perfect for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
