    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle body actuator service, ensuring the high-revving internal combustion assembly remains robust. The chassis maintains its composure via aluminum-intensive suspension components and EDC dampening. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, the mechanical integrity and throttle response remain sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience in a modern-classic package.",
      "price": 34500.0,
