    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable find for anyone seeking a blend of reliability and sophisticated style. Having been meticulously cared for, the exterior retains a deep, glossy finish that catches the light beautifully, with only the minor, inevitable signs of careful use that come with a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is clean and free of any significant wear, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs exceptionally smooth, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule that ensures it\u2019s ready for many more miles of worry-free driving. It handles with precision and offers a quiet, composed ride on both city streets and highways. This is a solid, honest car that has been driven with pride and is now looking for a new home where it will be equally appreciated.",
