    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a quintessential driver's machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit features crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and optimized valve timing through the double VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gear engagement, directing power through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with an eye toward longevity, including documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain factory suspension geometry and turn-in precision. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the performance envelope remains intact, offering a linear power band and exceptional tactile feedback through the hydraulic steering rack.",
